<br />

<br />
The new stuff is going to cost more to keep people busy longer.  That's all there is to it.  If you don't feel the things are worth the points compared to the old stuff...but the old stuff first.  Eventually, you'll hit the point where you feel these things are worthwhile.  And then you'll get them.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
