                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I remember when DC soloing with frogs in Seb was 'it' <img src="images/smiles/icon_razz.gif" alt="icon_razz.gif" border="0" />
<br />

<br />
Seriously though, it's just another option for people to take. As it is, there are a lot of people nearing max or what's useful, and most of them end up starting twinks and/or playing alts because they really have very little to improve on. Making GoD AA's so high priced allows people to work on their main for that much longer and still get some gratification out of it. If they all cost 2-4-6 and 3-6-9, it wouldnt be more than a few weeks, and most people would have the 'needed' GoD aa's maxed already.
<br />
We could be getting nothing, so I for one am happy that I can once again start looking forward to a 'new' AA.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=405101" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://home.earthlink.net/~daerius1/daeriussig.jpg" border="0" /></a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
