I make <span style="font-weight: bold">1 aa per 50 min</span> in Tier 2 (Valor) with 6 person groups
<br />

<br />
how?
<br />

<br />
I hunt in level 65 pickup groups (and I also use a DC pet)
<br />

<br />
we kill level 61/62 mobs (Crawlers,Spiders,Golems)
<br />

<br />
I pull for the group and my pulls are constant -- there is always a mob "lined up" in camp
<br />

<br />
your group will make slower exp if you have to wait for pulls
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
in Valor caves, you run out of mobs and I avoid the caves because I dont like waiting for mob respawn
<br />

<br />
in the Valor wastelands, theres tons of mobs
<br />

<br />

